data.description: Beautiful older home with great curb appeal with large open feel rooms on every floor.  High ceilings, large upper landing along with grand foyer.  A great flex room off the main dining for many uses. 1/4 bath on the main level with a nice three season porch.  A beautiful sitting area off the kitchen that has many options for use.  So much potential and so much square footage for all your needs.  A must to see.
